spider man: into the spider verse
summary: Something I’ve noticed after watching Spider-Verse for the 4th time
body:
Something I’ve noticed after watching Spider-Verse for the 4th time

Ok is it just me or did anybody else notice how when Peter B was fighting Doc Oc in her office that he kept constantly reassuring Miles that “he could handle this” and “I got this buddy” even as he was getting tossed around because just moments earlier in the vent Miles had told him he couldn’t stand by and watch another Spider-Man die

Peter B knew Miles wouldn’t get himself and the hard drive to safety unless he knew Spider-Man was going to make it though the fight so even if he was losing he made sure to keep telling Miles I got this it’s ok go

Did anyone else notice that??? cause I did and let me tell you I have feelings about it
